name: Linda Anderson
description: I am kind, devoted, loving, very exiting to live and to meet my beloved man! I am open minded, intelligent, caring, honest, strong, humble. I can generally see the funny side of life regardless. I am calm and enjoy life and growth is important to me. I love the outdoors, nature and sports. I love adventure and challenges. I like spending time with my dear life partner, .watching movies, going to sporting events.
